{"tid":2251559,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：挑機689「教師非唯一激進源頭」 劉鳴煒：社會不穩源於某官（李八方）","createTime":"2020-10-21T01:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T02:33:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3b88cdb3c59701b3d0035e7e332668f006c86a","tid":2251559,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:33:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/E2BCYWWRG5EK7GVIWA37X5FVZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FE2BCYWWRG5EK7GVIWA37X5FVZE%2F&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QePMooGStKW6IyA4tNg2jBs%3D&h=ff668963\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201021%2FE2BCYWWRG5EK7GVIWA37X5FVZE%2F&h=37024400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201021/E2BCYWWRG5EK7GVIWA37X5FVZE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：挑機689「教師非唯一激進源頭」<br />\n劉鳴煒：社會不穩源於某官（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/H1cHU70fw8wg-_OhSR6tjvtLoi0=/2007x842/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3UHSTAYYUNCGLJTHNQZMKPRFAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FH1cHU70fw8wg-_OhSR6tjvtLoi0%3D%2F2007x842%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3UHSTAYYUNCGLJTHNQZMKPRFAM.jpg&h=648cd4c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早排全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英加埋政府連環出手打壓老師，將反送中年輕人上街、學生對政府不滿瀨晒落老師度，以為咁就可以向中央交到貨，不過青年發展委員會副主席劉鳴煒就唔係好認同689等人嘅做法，認為將青年人激進嘅源頭講成係教師，係單一化同過份簡化，又話普遍市民同青年覺得，香港社會不穩源於特區政府或者某位官員，好多網民猜測，劉鳴煒講嘅某位官員係邊個呢？<br />\n<br />\n劉鳴煒噚日接受民主黨前主席劉慧卿嘅網台節目訪問時，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱社會復和要睇時機<br />\n<br />\n佢又話港版國安法立法後示威暴動係減少咗，短期社會安定咗，但要長期穩定就要解決人心問題，但要社會復和係要睇時機，要揀啱時機去做，對於689話青年人激進的源頭係教師、仲公開教師資料，劉鳴煒就唔多認同，佢承認教師對學生有好大影響力，要做好本份，但香港咩青年都有，激進、深藍都有，所以唔可以單一化或過份簡化分析，其他地方被激進化過程見到，通。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n劉鳴煒冇講某位官員係乜水，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"fd68eeb22183aaaefd290374428535ffca1eca8e","tid":2251559,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:35:36.000Z","msg":"條死廢老好撚記仇的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96552cb7eda2c07c3a7365e10dac05c996b5f23f","tid":2251559,"uid":29423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:35:48.000Z","msg":"大家都明係邊個<br />\n藍絲都唔撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42b8325cbc096f040bcef0aeb75fe3131f786eb","tid":2251559,"uid":70846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96552cb7eda2c07c3a7365e10dac05c996b5f23f","tid":2251559,"uid":29423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:35:48.000Z","msg":"大家都明係邊個<br />\n藍絲都唔撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:42:49.000Z","msg":"藍絲好多官都唔撐喎<br />\n唔計林鄭<br />\n仲有<br />\n張建忠<br />\n陳茂波<br />\n陳𦘦始<br />\n<br />\n不如直接歸類做成個政府啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c8a066a9a95d9bbed8c99ef496b2cfca9bc3af","tid":2251559,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:49:38.000Z","msg":"二世祖令我憎恨政府，黨安法呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bb07cbfb8a04e40cf93b6643a3bb37c2bcf807","tid":2251559,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87c8a066a9a95d9bbed8c99ef496b2cfca9bc3af","tid":2251559,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T01:49:38.000Z","msg":"二世祖令我憎恨政府，黨安法呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:33:22.000Z","msg":"唔拉二世祖<br />\n點對得住快必 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}